thread.title: MOVES-Ernst & Young hires former eBay executive Jeff Wong
thread.title_full: MOVES-Ernst & Young hires former eBay executive Jeff Wong | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: MOVES-Ernst & Young hires former eBay executive Jeff Wong
text:
July 23 Audit firm Ernst & Young LLP appointed Jeff Wong as global chief innovation officer.
Wong will lead Ernst & Young's newly created global innovation team, the company said.
He joins from eBay Inc, where he was founder and senior director of eBay's business incubation group. (Reporting by Anet Josline Pinto in Bengaluru)
